<p>Working in coordination with other state-of-the-art support departments like Cardiology, Neurology, Nephrology, Ophthalmology, Radiology, Physiotherapy and Yoga, the Diabetology unit of Chellaram Diabetes Institute aspires to become a Centre of Excellence and a referral center in <strong>Diabetes</strong>.</p>
